Config.Description:
Listening port required for computer-to-computer connections.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span class='label-important'&gt;Note:&lt;/span&gt; Please note that this setting is only important &lt;b&gt;IF&lt;/b&gt; you change your network type to &lt;b&gt;Bridge&lt;/b&gt;, which is highly discouraged.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span class='label-warning'&gt;Tip:&lt;/span&gt; This port can be changed using the webUI, on Settings &gt; General &gt; Inbound backup from other computers.
